snippet.textDisplay:
I'm the kind of person who doesn't really believe in marriage or having kids, but I love these kinds of videos that are so authentic, realistic, and pure. Seeing other people love in so many different but happy ways makes my heart happy and hopeful. I actually do love someone right now and hope to be a better partner for them soon, one day. Maybe marriage and kids won't ever happen for me, but love and happiness is something that everyone deserves.

Oh, and self love, too!!!! Married or not, dating or not, always remember to dance with yourself ❤
